			  	What you do is completely valid, nothing to worry about. This is however, a very slow method... notice that for lvl 20 you need 190,000 XP... that means 190 training missions, each takes 2 hours. Even if you were a bot and resent the fleets every 2 hours, you would need 16 days to train your commanders to max. Forget about it ;)<br />
<br />
Training is good for initial levels... like 4-6, maybe 7-8 max if you're very stubborn. Later it's just pointless, because you can get much much more XP in battles. What costs several days of training can be gained in one battle... <p><br>--<br />
&lt;3 djx			   <P align=right></P>
